title: Executive Order 7482-Designating Morehead City, North Carolina, as a Customs Port of Entry
content: By virtue of and pursuant to the authority vested in me by the act of August 1, 1914, 38 Stat. 609, 623 (U.S.C., title 19, sec. 2), I hereby designate Morehead City, North Carolina, as a customs port of entry in Customs Collection District No. 15 (North Carolina), effective this date.
citation: Franklin D. Roosevelt, Executive Order 7482-Designating Morehead City, North Carolina, as a Customs Port of Entry Online by Gerhard Peters and John T. Woolley, The American Presidency Project https://www.presidency.ucsb.edu/node/210095
